one_reviews_text: The graphics are not the best.  The rollercoaster rides are not a very long.  While each of the 3 rides are similar, each brings something new to the table.  I liked the creativity in the 3 rides.  I think it's worth the $2, especially for VR rollercoaster enthusiasts.

review_feedback: Hi DudaMaria, Nice to know that you had fun. Thank you very much for your review!
